name: PAPER FLOWERS
description:
What's the best kind of flower? One that never wilts or dies! These flowers are made out of paper and will last forever! They are each handmade and look just like real flowers! Use them as decorations,use them as chair bows, stick them in a bowl, pin them to fabric, the uses are endless! I can make these in any color or size that you would like. Flowers are priced as follows:

$2 each
contact me for discounts on bulk orders

Due to the fragile nature of this item they can get a little bruised in transit but don't worry! Just fluff them up a little an they will be as good as new!

name: ORIGAMI BOUQUETS
description:
These were the bouquets I used for my own wedding and they were a huge hit! You don't have to worry about them dying and best of all they are WAY less expensive than real flowers! They also make great boutonnieres, hair flowers, or just great decorations in general! These can be made in any color you want!

$3 per flower
contact me for discounts on bulk orders

name: POP ART PAINTINGS
description:
want a cool gift to give a friend or some new artwork for your home? I can take your personal pictures and turn them into pop art! It can be a picture of almost anything, just email me your picture and I will show you a sample of what the painting will look like. The paintings are either black, white, and gray or shades of a chosen color. for example, if you want a red color scheme, the painting will have reds, pinks, and white, etc. All paintings are done on canvas using acrylic paint.

36"x28" canvas: $75 (other sizes also available, please contact me for pricing)

name: RECYCLED LENS NECKLACE
description:
